			</classificationInformation>
			<CASNumber>7775-14-6</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Sodium hydrosulfite is a strong reducing agent used in bleaching recycled pulp. It effectively reacts with the dyes in the pulp. It is also used as a non-aggressive alternative to bleach for removing color from dyed fabrics and for whitening antique textiles. It is a white, crystalline, water-soluble powder with the odour of sulfur dioxide.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">亚硫酸氢钠是一种用于漂白回收纸浆的强还原剂。它能有效地与纸浆中的染料发生反应。它还可作为漂白剂的一种非侵蚀性替代品，用于去除染色织物的颜色和增白古董纺织品。它是一种白色结晶性水溶性粉末，带有二氧化硫的气味。</common:generalComment>
